  "description": "<h3>Back of box - Game Boy Color (from <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/force-21_/adblurbs\">Ad Blurbs</a>)</h3><b>PREPARE FOR WWIII</b><br><br>The year is 2015 - World War III is about to begin. Technology has made nuclear weapons obsolete, leaving wars to be fought the conventional way with artillery, air support and infantry. You must choose Chinese or American forces to command. Plot your strategy and lead your platoon - You have a way to win!<br><br><li>One of the first Real Time Strategy War Games for the Game Boy Color.\n<li>Battle the enemy over 16 different levels including Desert, Countryside and Snowfields.\n<li>Command 8 different types of units including Air Support and Infantry.\n<li>Take out bridges to halt the enemy advance.\n<li>Position or Camouflage your Units to ambush enemy convoys.\n<li>Extremely simple interface lets the player jump quickly into the action.\n<li>Capture key strategic points to receive additional intelligence info.",
